{
  "id": "5eba97801629700022878d34",
  "title": "容器のメタファーと道のメタファー",
  "created": 1589286786,
  "updated": 1642153671,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5eba97801629700022878d34",
      "text": "容器のメタファーと道のメタファー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286786,
      "updated": 1589286790
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba9781aff09e0000ded9cc",
      "text": "[容器のメタファー]と[道のメタファー]がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286786,
      "updated": 1589286844
    },
    {
      "id": "61287671aff09e000095ef23",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041714,
      "updated": 1630041714
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba97bbaff09e0000ded9ce",
      "text": "Scrapbox以前のEvernoteなどメンタルモデルを引きずってる人はタグを「容器」として使いがち。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286844,
      "updated": 1589286847
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba97bfaff09e0000ded9cf",
      "text": "　例えば「本」ってタグを読書メモ全部につけて回る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286847,
      "updated": 1630041721
    },
    {
      "id": "61287678aff09e000095ef24",
      "text": "　これはタグを「本に関するページが入る容器」と認識している。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041721,
      "updated": 1630041725
    },
    {
      "id": "61287680aff09e000095ef25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041728,
      "updated": 1630041729
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba97c1aff09e0000ded9d0",
      "text": "でもshokaiとかの話を聞いてるとしばしば「リンク」「つながる」「たどる」という表現が出てくる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286850,
      "updated": 1630042391
    },
    {
      "id": "61287902aff09e0000f0365a",
      "text": "\t[人は場所を緯度経度ではなく道筋で覚える]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630042370,
      "updated": 1630042371
    },
    {
      "id": "612876b5aff09e00006ef93f",
      "text": "\t\tこれは[道のメタファー] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041782,
      "updated": 1630042378
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba97c5aff09e0000ded9d1",
      "text": "\t\t[リンクは道]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286853,
      "updated": 1630042395
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba97c6aff09e0000ded9d2",
      "text": " 「[どこでもドア]」というメタファーもそう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286855,
      "updated": 1630041795
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba97e3aff09e0000ded9d3",
      "text": " \t道がつながってなくてたどれない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286884,
      "updated": 1630041839
    },
    {
      "id": "612876eeaff09e000095ef26",
      "text": " \t→ドアを出して、行きたいところに近そうな文字列を入れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041839,
      "updated": 1630041841
    },
    {
      "id": "612876f0aff09e000095ef27",
      "text": " \t→実際に行ける所の中からいくつかサジェストしてくれる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041841,
      "updated": 1630041843
    },
    {
      "id": "612876f2aff09e000095ef28",
      "text": " \t→選ぶと道がつながる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041843,
      "updated": 1630041843
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba9833aff09e0000ded9d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286964,
      "updated": 1589286964
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba9804aff09e0000ded9d5",
      "text": "「検索をより良くしたい」的な話をよく聞く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286917,
      "updated": 1630041872
    },
    {
      "id": "61287711aff09e000095ef2a",
      "text": " それって自動車が生まれつつある時代に「もっと速い馬が欲しい」って言うようなもん",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041873,
      "updated": 1630041886
    },
    {
      "id": "61287719aff09e000095ef2b",
      "text": " 慣れてるからって理由で馬に固執するのが問題なんじゃないの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041881,
      "updated": 1630041896
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba9831aff09e0000ded9d6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286962,
      "updated": 1589286962
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba9845aff09e0000ded9d8",
      "text": "「Scrapboxって習得コストが高い」みたいなセリフ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286981,
      "updated": 1630041906
    },
    {
      "id": "61287732aff09e000095ef2c",
      "text": "　明示的に学習の必要な記法とかは大した量ではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041906,
      "updated": 1630041910
    },
    {
      "id": "61287736aff09e000095ef2d",
      "text": "　本当にハードルになってるのは明示的でない「メンタルモデルの変化」だと思う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041910,
      "updated": 1630041916
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba9845aff09e0000ded9d9",
      "text": " で、メンタルモデルが変化した方がScrapboxを便利に使える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589286981,
      "updated": 1630041927
    },
    {
      "id": "61287746aff09e000095ef2e",
      "text": " 　のだが、notaの経営上は「メンタルモデルが変化しないと使えない」よりは「変化しなくても使える」が選ばれる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041927,
      "updated": 1630041929
    },
    {
      "id": "61287749aff09e000095ef2f",
      "text": " 　その結果、メンタルモデルが変化しないままでもそれなりに使えてしまうから、変化の必要がわかりにくくなる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630041929,
      "updated": 1630041929
    },
    {
      "id": "5eba9878aff09e0000ded9de",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1589287033,
      "updated": 1589287033
    },
    {
      "id": "61e1463aaff09e00001fd495",
      "text": "表記揺れ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1642153577,
      "updated": 1642153660
    },
    {
      "id": "61287337aff09e000095ef22",
      "text": "　[箱のメタファー]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630040888,
      "updated": 1630040895
    },
    {
      "id": "61287337aff09e000095ef21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1630040887,
      "updated": 1630040887
    },
    {
      "id": "61e146bcaff09e00001a3d28",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1642153661,
      "updated": 1642153669
    },
    {
      "id": "61e146c4aff09e00001a3d2a",
      "text": "\t[切り口を発見して行動]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1642153669,
      "updated": 1642153670
    },
    {
      "id": "61e146c4aff09e00001a3d29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1642153669,
      "updated": 1642153669
    }
  ]
}